note: Ogbah has struggled this season and is in line to see a sharp reduction in snaps with Bradley Chubb now in town. He may have deep league bye week filler appeal for Week 9, but fantasy managers will want to make other plans where feasible.

Herring should see an expanded role with Frank Clark serving as suspension, as he is expected to be the top reserve behind George Karlaftis and Carlos Dunlap. He is worth a look at a DL3 option in 16+ team leagues or as a desperation play for 12 team managers dealing with a heavy bye.
